OL,3,CLloyds to put all 67,000 staff through
OL,4,CAI training in fresh digital push
OL,6,FLloyds Banking Group is putting its
OL,7,F67,000-strong workforce through
OL,8,Fartificial intelligence (AI) training
OL,9,Fas part of a multi-million pound drive
OL,10,Fto adopt the technology.
OL,12,FAll employees of the banking group
OL,13,Fwill be expected to complete the
OL,14,Fcourse by the end of the year.
OL,16,FThe new AI Academy comes on the back
OL,17,Fof chief executive Charlie Nunn and
OL,18,Fhis entire executive committee being
OL,19,Fenrolled into a bespoke training
OL,20,Fprogramme in a push to drive change
OL,21,Ffrom the top of the organisation.
