OL,3,CLloyds to put all 67,000 staff through
OL,4,CAI training in fresh digital push
OL,6,FThe decision to put all staff through
OL,7,Ftraining, regardless of their role or
OL,8,Fseniority, marks a significant step
OL,9,Fforward in the bank's digital overhaul.
OL,11,FTo begin, employees will complete a
OL,12,Fshort module on "working with AI
OL,13,Fresponsibly", which teaches about the
OL,14,Fsafe and ethical use of the technology
OL,15,Fin line with the standards set out by
OL,16,Fthe bank.
