OL,3,CLloyds to put all 67,000 staff through
OL,4,CAI training in fresh digital push
OL,6,FLloyds hopes to train its workforce to
OL,7,Futilise the technology in their day-to-
OL,8,Fway work, with the aim of saving time,
OL,9,Fproviding new services for customers
OL,10,Fand potentially bringing in more money.
OL,12,FIt has invested several million pounds
OL,13,Finto such initiatives and wants 100%
OL,14,Fof its workforce to be "AI literate"
OL,15,Fby the end of 2026.
OL,17,FIt comes at a time when the group `
OL,18,Fwhich incorporates Lloyds, Halifax and
OL,19,FBank of Scotland ` has been trimming
OL,20,Fback its branch network and
OL,21,Foverhauling its IT division.
